6
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,640
Jianjian, speak.

7
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,160
Dad.

8
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,440
What's wrong?

9
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,880
Why are you so low-spirited?

10
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,200
It's like you're dying.

11
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,680
I took a hit.

12
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,200
Tell me. What happened?

13
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,079
Well...

14
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,000
Well...

15
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,440
I can't tell you now.

16
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:48,840
I'll tell you later.

17
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,000
You're keeping it secret from me?

18
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,079
Then why did you call me?

19
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:59,520
I need to be encouraged to face it.

20
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,240
I need you to cheer me on

21
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,040
like refueling a car with gas.

22
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,680
You need me to

23
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,480
refuel your car?

24
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,200
Don't you

25
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,240
run a gas station yourself?

26
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,040
Doesn’t our whole family

27
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,960
always go to your place to refuel?

28
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:19,280
My gas station is running out of gas now.

29
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,360
Really?

30
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,720
It has moments when it runs out of gas?

31
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:27,000
OK. Wait a moment.

32
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,560
I'll call someone now.

33
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:32,040
Is it a gas company?

34
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,800
I'm Li Haichao.

35
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,640
I need you to do me a little favor.

36
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,920
My daughter's gas station is

37
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:40,800
out of gas.

38
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,560
Assign some to her.

39
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,840
How much can you give her?

40
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:48,360
Five trucks? That's too little.

41
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,520
Give her 50 trucks of it at least.

42
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:52,520
When can it be delivered?

43
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,840
OK, tomorrow morning.

44
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:56,560
Thanks.

45
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,440
Come to my restaurant and enjoy my noodles when you have time.

46
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,800
OK.

47
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,200
Jianjian, did you hear that?

48
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,960
It's taken care of.

49
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:07,000
Your gas will be full when you open your eyes

50
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,040
tomorrow morning.

51
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,800
Thank you, Dad.

52
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,880
You're welcome.

53
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:15,920
Dad.

54
