Think about it.

95
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,560
With you like this,

96
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,000
if you have your child,

97
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,960
who is naughtier than you,

98
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:48,120
should I help you with parenting?

99
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:49,040
Maybe not.

100
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,760
I'd choose to go to the nursing home

101
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,640
to enjoy the happiness of leisure.

102
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,280
Well, yeah.

103
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:57,960
Alright.

104
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,880
Stop speculating the future.

105
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:00,600
Just go to bed.

106
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,280
Bye.

107
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,080
