Song, show the patient where to get the medicine.

123
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,280
OK.

124
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,800
What brings you here?

125
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,120
I want to treat you to lunch.

126
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:18,600
I've been waiting for you

127
