Eat!

134
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:37,840
Go ahead.

135
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,480
Do you have anything to talk to me?

136
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,520
No.

137
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,080
Eat.

138
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,080
Then we'll go back to work.

139
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:47,440
I have a lot to do in the studio this afternoon.

140
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,200
You came over at noon

141
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,320
just to eat with me?

142
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,640
Or else?

143
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:56,240
From now on, every day, as long as I have time,

144
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,320
I will come to eat with you.

145
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,280
In the afternoon,

146
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,720
I'll try to finish work early

147
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,800
to go home with you.

148
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,800
You don't need to go to my place for me.

149
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,360
Come on.

150
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,200
I'll accompany you to take a taxi first.

151
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,080
No need.

152
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,160
It's so close.

153
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,360
I can walk back.

154
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,360
You can go back now.

155
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,120
What's wrong?

156
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,320
Why are you doing this all of a sudden?

157
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:36,200
Don't you want me to pity you?

158
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,520
I am pitying you now.

159
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,240
