161
00:08:43,549 --> 00:08:44,640
Don't think so much.

162
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:45,960
Why should you?

163
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,480
Put all that intelligence

164
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,720
into the right place.

165
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,960
You can as well

166
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,760
see more patients.

167
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,480
Don't worry.

168
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,040
I'll take pity on you

169
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,440
as much as I can.

170
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,160
I'll pity you till you feel that

171
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:58,920
you don't need it anymore.

172
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,320
Then I will continue to pity you,

173
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,360
because I just like to

174
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,360
pity someone.

175
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:03,240
OK?

176
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:05,920
Are you still mad?

177
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:06,520
No.

178
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,000
You even cried yesterday.

179
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:09,840
No, I didn't.

180
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:10,680
OK. You didn't.

181
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,960
That was just a puppy peeing.

182
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,560
What puppy?

183
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,320
See you. I'll go to your place this evening.

184
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,520
No need.

185
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:19,000
Dad called me

186
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,680
and asked me to

187
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:20,720
accompany him to see a traditional Chinese medicine (TCM) doctor in the evening.

188
