189
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,520
He said he doesn’t feel well.

190
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:26,080
OK. Approved.

191
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:26,680
Go ahead.

192
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,720
Why are you so tall?

193
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:43,160
♫Like a breeze♫

194
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:47,280
♫A breeze with words to say♫

195
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,680
♫I see♫

196
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:50,320
♫Actually♫

197
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:54,240
♫I'm in love more than I think♫

198
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,520
Bye.

199
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:57,560
♫Realize, realize♫

200
00:09:57,560 --> 00:10:01,960
♫Everything around me♫

201
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:06,240
♫Is love♫

