203
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,920
It kept me busy.

204
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,880
What time does the traditional Chinese medicine clinic close today?

205
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:39,440
Are we late?

206
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,160
No.

207
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,680
The doctor is my friend.

208
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,280
And the clinic belongs to him.

209
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,360
I just called.

210
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,320
He's waiting for us.

211
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,440
Dad.

212
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,320
What is your ailment?

213
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,720
How about going to the hospital for a physical examination?

214
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,640
No need.

215
