The physical examination that my unit just bought for me last month

216
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,680
found nothing wrong.

217
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,320
But recently,

218
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,320
for some reason,

219
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:02,080
I feel uncomfortable all over my body.

220
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,760
Sometimes, you have to try traditional Chinese medicine.

221
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:06,200
Give it some credit.

222
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:08,600
Let's go.

223
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,760
Nothing is wrong.

224
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,640
It's hot recently,

225
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,360
and your spleen and stomach are weakened.

226
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:21,640
I'll prescribe you sanfutie

227
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,800
(medicated patches placed on acupuncture points on the body for treating illnesses during the hottest period).

228
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,960
Dr. Zhao, that can wait.

229
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:26,360
Please...

230
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,560
check on my son.

231
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:28,880
He hasn't been able to sleep well recently.

232
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:30,720
I don't need to be checked. I'm fine.

233
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,080
Come on. You're already here.

234
