Sometimes four or five hours.

247
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,240
Sometimes five or six hours.

248
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:11,680
This is due to the incoordination between spleen and stomach

249
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:13,320
and stagnation of liver qi.

250
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,760
Stagnation of liver qi?

251
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:16,880
My son is so young.

252
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:18,280
How can he have that?

253
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,560
He doesn't drink too much.

254
