273
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,120
My son is not ill.

274
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,160
He just can't sleep well.

275
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,480
Why does he need a psychiatrist?

276
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:58,760
Bad sleep quality

277
00:12:58,760 --> 00:12:59,440
has a lot to do

278
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,680
with mental stress.

279
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,680
