280
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,040
to see whether there are organic lesions.

281
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,760
What are you talking about?

282
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,320
That's enough.

283
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,600
Oh, take back your words.

284
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,520
